<div>MakerFaire is on the horizon, and that means the Power Racing Series Grand Finale is too! This is a competition (in the loosest sense of the word) where nerds from across the land, take plastic Power Wheels cars and trick them out to make them go really fast. Silliness ensues.  <a href="http://www.powerracingseries.org/" target="_blank">http://www.powerracingseries.org/</a></div>
<div>We here at the MakerBar have gotten our hands on this shiny FIRETRUCK!! WE NEED YOUR HELP!!!</div>
