<div><b><span style="font-size: large">VOLUNTEER FOR THE MAKERBAR POWER WHEELS RACE TEAM!</span></b></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div>You do not need to be a member of the MakerBar to join. There will be a working session on Sat 8/24 from 6:00 pm − 10:00 pm at MakerBar.  SIGNUP FOR THIS EVENT ON <a href="http://meetup.com/" target="_blank">MEETUP.COM</a> - <a href="http://www.meetup.com/MakerBar/events/134112602/" target="_blank">http://www.meetup.com/MakerBar/events/134112602/</a></div>
<div><span style="font-size: 13px">This will be the cut off date for MakerBar Power Wheels 2013. If we do not have enough volunteers by then… Well, we will have a very early start on the 2014 team!!</span></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div><span style="font-size: 13px">What are we doing? We are building an electric car based on a children’s toy firetruck (see above pic[s]) to race in the Maker Faire PowerRacing Series at Maker Faire 2013 on September 21-22 at New York Hall of Science, Queens, NY.  </span></div>
<div></div>
<div><a href="http://www.powerracingseries.org/" target="_blank">http://www.powerracingseries.org/</a></div>
