<div></div>
<div>Thank you to everyone that as joined in so far. MakerBar Membership (&lt;20) is stretched a little thin for this event (with the MakerBar table to host all weekend). We are gong to be heavily reliant on volunteers for our Power Wheels team.</div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div>At this point <b>we do not have enough volunteers</b> to finish the build or field a race team at MakerFaire 2013… so please sign up now and join the team.</div>
<div></div>
<div><span style="text-decoration: underline">Power Wheels Team:</span></div>
<div></div>
<div>We need at least 4 qualified/skilled leaders/workers/assistants for each of the four systems:</div>
<div>- POWER - electric system, motors, batteries, chargers, kill switch</div>
<div>- WHEELS - frame, wheels, steering, braking, seat attachment</div>
<div>- SAFTEY - steering wheel, seat, safety harness, brake controls, kill switch controls, Wheelie BAR!!!!!</div>
<div>- MOXIE - blingity-bling-bling, lights, siren, water canon, etc., numbers, moxie board tag (see rules), team flag</div>
<div></div>
<div>Even better would be 10-12 people with each one taking just one piece of the build.</div>
<div></div>
<div><b>Weekend of Maker Faire 9/20, 9/21, 9/22:</b></div>
