<div>Also, we have to get a team member to be part-time help to run the races. You get a cool t-shirt. This would be best if it was one of the assistants. Cannot be the driver. or chief mechanic. (See rules.) We are looking for 7-8 people on the team. [But, with the right 5 very committed people we could get it done.] It really depends on people’s skills and availability.</div>
